{"data":[{"date":"07:42 12/07","title":"\"Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Croatia v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/harry-kane-khong-the-ghi-ban-truoc-thuy-dien-va-croatia-vi-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.</h2><h2>\u0110T Anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kieran Trippier \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Ivan Perisic t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Croatia \u1edf ph\u00fat 68. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mandzukic \u1edf ph\u00fat 109.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/pickford-dt-anh-da-phai-tra-gia-vi-phung-phi-co-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T&nbsp;Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pickford cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thi\u1ebfu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Croatia c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong hi\u1ec7p hai&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pickford c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Croatia do c\u00f4ng Perisic. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Perisic \u0111\u00e3 gi\u01a1 ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngang t\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;B\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Walker \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i cao ch\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia-465-191003.html\">Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1165","checkdouble":"191000"},{"date":"07:25 12/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (12/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1272018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 12/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang 