argin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i c\u01a1n t\u1ee9c khi Croatia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Croatia. M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c Croatia hao t\u1ed5n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c khi hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric phan phao truyen thong Anh sau khi DT Croatia gianh chien thang.\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau khi \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau khi \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong 120 ph\u00fat, Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p Croatia v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m to l\u1edbn&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Croatia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 n\u00f3i 'OK, h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd cho th\u1ea5y ai m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi'. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i, h\u1ecd n\u00ean khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo-421-190991.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo-421-190991.html\">Ivan Perisic: V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup ng\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00fap \u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup khi\u1ebfn Luka Modric kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u1eb3ng ai m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ea3. Croatia ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u1ecdi kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ebd ra \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y v\u1eabn phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Sau th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed th\u1ec3 thao Croatia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-khong-the-ghi-ban-truoc-thuy-dien-va-croatia-vi-chan-thuong-421-191000.html\">Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Croatia v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/mario-mandzukic-xo-nga-phong-vien-anh-465-190999.html\">M\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh, Mandzukic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-that-bai-truoc-croatia-that-dau-don-421-190996.html\">Harry Kane: Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia th\u1eadt \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-dt-croatia-lam-nen-lich-su-465-190995.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1163","checkdouble":"191003"},{"date":"08:13 12/07","title":"Pickford: \"\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/pickford-dt-anh-da-phai-tra-gia-vi-phung-phi-co-hoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.</h2><h2>\u0110T Anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kieran Trippier \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Ivan Perisic t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Croatia \u1edf ph\u00fat 68. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mandzukic \u1edf ph\u00fat 109.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/pickford-dt-anh-da-phai-tra-gia-vi-phung-phi-co-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T&nbsp;Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pickford cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thi\u1ebfu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Croatia c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong hi\u1ec7p hai&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pickford c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Croatia do c\u00f4ng Perisic. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Perisic \u0111\u00e3 gi\u01a1 ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngang t\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;B\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Walker \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i cao ch\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia-465-191003.html\">Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1162","checkdouble":"191007"},{"date":"08:21 12/07","title":"Mario Mandzukic g\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 \"ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/mario-mandzukic-goi-chien-thang-cua-dt-croatia-la-phep-mau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mario Mandzukic g\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u sau khi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Croatia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Mario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 hai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Mandzukic an mung cuong nhiet sau ban thang an dinh chien thang cho DT Croatia.\" title=\"Mario Mandzukic \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110T Croatia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mario-mandzukic-goi-chien-thang-cua-dt-croatia-la-phep-mau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mario Mandzukic g\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u&quot; - Mario Mandzukic th\u1ed1t l\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: &quot;Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Anh. T\u1ed1i nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 s\u01b0 t\u1eed v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m th\u1ebf trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u01af\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Mandzukic<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0110T Croatia hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Mandzukic c\u00f2n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Davor Suker kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi \u0111i xa nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u1edf World Cup 1998.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo-421-190991.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo-421-190991.html\">Ivan Perisic: V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup ng\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Mandzukic th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u1ea5p \u1ee7 t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m b\u00e9: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi qu\u1ed1c gia nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 Croatia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1eadm nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Hai m\u01b0\u01a1i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Omis. T\u00f4i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Croatia, ch\u1ec9 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pickford-dt-anh-da-phai-tra-gia-vi-phung-phi-co-hoi-469-191007.html\">Pickford: \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia-465-191003.html\">Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-khong-the-ghi-ban-truoc-thuy-dien-va-croatia-vi-chan-thuong-421-191000.html\">Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Croatia v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/mario-mandzukic-xo-nga-phong-vien-anh-465-190999.html\">M\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh, Mandzukic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1161","checkdouble":"191008"},{"date":"08:34 12/07","title":"HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau m\u00e0n t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/hlv-southgate-bao-ve-kane-sau-man-tang-hinh-truoc-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi g\u00ec h\u01a1n t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane sau khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Croatia.</h2><h2>Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kane nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKane kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u00e0o khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Lovren \u2013 Vida c\u1ee7a Croatia. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n th\u00ec Kane l\u1ea1i phung ph\u00ed m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Kane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Southgate v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau m\u00e0n t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau m\u00e0n t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/hlv-southgate-bao-ve-kane-sau-man-tang-hinh-truoc-croatia.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau khi \u0110T\u00a0Anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cKane \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian trong hi\u1ec7p hai ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong hi\u1ec7p hai v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cKane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng su\u1ed1t 3 tu\u1ea7n qua\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Southgate khen ng\u1ee3i Croatia</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Southgate t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Croatia v\u00e0 \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Vatreni l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec l\u00e0m cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cCroatia s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i luy\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. \u0110\u00f4i khi, kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qua hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho Croatia. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u1ec1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i 120 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft n\u00f3i l\u00ean kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Croatia hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<strong><br />\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1160","checkdouble":"191009"},{"date":"08:56 12/07","title":"Sao Croatia: T\u01b0\u1edfng Anh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn v\u1eady!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Sime Vrsaljko l\u00ean m\u1eb7t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam S\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nguy\u00ean h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Sime Vrsaljko l\u00ean m\u1eb7t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam S\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nguy\u00ean h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span> v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn Croatia th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vrsaljko tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vrsaljko tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vrsaljko tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao c\u0169ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi, g\u1eafn k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tr\u1ebb trung v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Sime Vrsaljko v\u1eabn th\u1ea3n nhi\u00ean x\u00e1t mu\u1ed1i n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng khi \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Atletico sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2u \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc ng\u1ee3i ca th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u1ebf n\u1ecd, r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i n\u1eefa, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eadt r\u1ed3i. Kh\u00f4ng, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng pressing tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa th\u00ec h\u00f3a ra h\u1ecd l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 c\u0169 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e0nh t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9, trong khi Croatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nEuro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Gareth Southgate h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean tr\u1eadn thua Croatia t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1159","checkdouble":"191010"},{"date":"08:44 12/07","title":"H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia thi nhau pose \u1ea3nh \u0103n m\u1eebng l\u00ean MXH","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/ha-guc-anh-cau-thu-croatia-pose-anh-an-mung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px 