r>\r\n            <td>Ante Rebic &quot;t\u1ef1 s\u01b0\u1edbng&quot; c\u00f9ng HLV Zlatko Dalic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Rakitic cung tranh thu chup anh cung ong thay Zlatko Dalic trong ngay chien thang.\" title=\"Ivan Rakitic c\u0169ng tranh th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Zlatko Dalic trong ng\u00e0y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/4E240CBC00000578-5944363-Dalic_held_up_the_Croatia_flag_with_Barcelona_midfielder_Ivan_Ra-a-38_1531351590690.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ivan Rakitic c\u0169ng tranh th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Zlatko Dalic trong ng\u00e0y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vedran Corluka mung chien thang cung cac dong doi Luka Modric, Brozovic va Mateo Kovacic.\" title=\"Vedran Corluka m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Luka Modric, Brozovic v\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/4E240C5800000578-5944363-Vedran_Corluka_second_from_right_with_Luka_Modric_right_Brozovic-a-34_1531351541362.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vedran Corluka m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Luka Modric, Brozovic v\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-bao-ve-kane-sau-man-tang-hinh-truoc-croatia-469-191009.html\">HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau m\u00e0n t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/mario-mandzukic-goi-chien-thang-cua-dt-croatia-la-phep-mau-465-191008.html\">Mario Mandzukic g\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pickford-dt-anh-da-phai-tra-gia-vi-phung-phi-co-hoi-469-191007.html\">Pickford: \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia-465-191003.html\">Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-khong-the-ghi-ban-truoc-thuy-dien-va-croatia-vi-chan-thuong-421-191000.html\">Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Croatia v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/mario-mandzukic-xo-nga-phong-vien-anh-465-190999.html\">M\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh, Mandzukic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1158","checkdouble":"191012"},{"date":"04:35 12/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anh d\u00f9 d\u1eabn b\u00e0n s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 Kieran Trippier \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Tam s\u01b0 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa, h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1ecd n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1ecd n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh thua Croatia 1-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o. Khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t th\u00ec Croatia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ph\u00fat 68, Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n30 ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Croatia gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 109, Perisic chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro.<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\" target=\"_blank\"> K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh </span>gi\u00fap Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Euro v\u00e0 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh d\u00f9 d\u1eabn b\u00e0n s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jamie Carragher\" title=\"Jamie Carragher\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/clip-soc-huyen-thoai-liverpool-nho-nuoc-bot-vao-fan-mu-sau-dai-chien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jamie Carragher khen ng\u1ee3i Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Jamie Carragher c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCroatia ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi d\u00e2n s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 4 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan, Patrick Kluivert chia s\u1ebb: \u201cS\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Croatia. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong 65 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU, Rio Ferdinand cho r\u1eb1ng: \u201cAnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng, h\u00f4m nay kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh, Gary Lineker \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Tam s\u01b0: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1157","checkdouble":"190990"},{"date":"04:58 12/07","title":"Ivan Perisic: \"V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup ng\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi anh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIvan Perisic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Croatia ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Ivan-Perisic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Croatia-vs-Anh-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Croatia ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Inter Milan b\u0103ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Kyle Walker trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pickford, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 109, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 Mario Mandzukic b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Pickford gi\u00fap Croatia ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Croatia vs Anh </span>ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Perisic g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi Perisic nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World\u00a0Cup 2018 v\u1edbi anh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic da co 4 ban o cac ky World Cup\" title=\"Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic v\u1eabn ng\u1ee1 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang m\u01a1 sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Anh, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng\".</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia ch\u1ec9 4 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3. 20 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang ng\u1ee1 m\u00ecnh m\u01a1 v\u1eady\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra qu\u00e1 nhanh khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia 2-1 Anh<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Croatia 2-1 Anh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia 2-1 Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Thong-so-Anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia 2-1 Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1156","checkdouble":"190991"},{"date":"05:31 12/07","title":"HLV Croatia l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/hlv-croatia-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-thang-anh-trong-tran-ban-ket.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Croatia t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed nh\u01b0 m\u1edf h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf Moscow, hay xa h\u01a1n \u1edf ch\u00ednh qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 khi \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup.\r\n\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div