diaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gareth Southgate th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 khi \u0110T Anh qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng Tam S\u01b0 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh non tr\u1ebb l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng sau 120 ph\u00fat, qua \u0111\u00f3 ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i r\u1eddi Moscow \u0111\u1ec3 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1edbi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate noi sau tran thua cua DT Anh tai ban ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"HLV Gareth Southgate n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Gareth Southgate n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. HLV Gareth Southgate n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh: &quot;Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn n\u1ed7i \u0111au th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 ai mu\u1ed1n \u1edf t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng?&quot;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ai ch\u1eb3ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00fam l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y. Ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 n\u01a1i th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. \u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 26, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Tam S\u01b0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ed1n n\u0103m n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190990.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190990.html\">Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span><br>\r\nAnh d\u00f9 d\u1eabn b\u00e0n s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady sau n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, HLV Gareth Southgate b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eaft t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai: &quot;Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i v\u1eabn n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd so v\u1edbi hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, c\u1ea3 qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-thang-anh-trong-tran-ban-ket-465-190992.html\">HLV Croatia l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo-421-190991.html\">Ivan Perisic: V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup ng\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-them-dai-chien-anh-vs-croatia-mandzukic-de-doa-pickford-421-190978.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs Croatia, Mandzukic '\u0111e d\u1ecda' Pickford</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-anh-463-190974.html\">Croatia 2-1 Anh: Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1154","checkdouble":"190993"},{"date":"06:06 12/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Mario Mandzukic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus ch\u1ec9 ghi 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Binh-luan-Croatia-vs-Anh-ban-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mandzukic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean vai \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luka Modric. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMandzukic ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Perisic. Anh x\u1eed l\u00fd tinh t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c kh\u00f4ng cho Pickford m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Anh n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n n\u1eefa Mandzukic m\u1edbi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n. Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 Perisic l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Raheem Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, HLV Gareth Southgate ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Raheem Sterling \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Harry Kane trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling tiep tuc co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Sterling ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 22 l\u1ea7n, tung ra 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat anh ra \u1edf ph\u00fat 73 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Marcus Rashford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Sterling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018 Sterling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh 5 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi n\u1ed5i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Les Bleus thong dong ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Phap vs Uruguay\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Du-am-Phap-vs-Uruguay-Les-Bleus-quet-sach-Nam-My-bang-hai-bo-mat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Croatia \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n Croatia 1 ng\u00e0y, v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 ng\u00e0y/tr\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup 2018 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 1 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps c\u00f2n vui h\u01a1n th\u1ebf b\u1edfi Croatia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nModric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i o\u1eb1n m\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Modric v\u00e0 Mandzukic b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb chu\u1ed9t r\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c b\u1ecb t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, Croatia s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. B\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a l\u0103n nh\u01b0ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Les Bleus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Kyle Walker</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyle Walker s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. Anh ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Harry Maguire v\u00e0 John Stones \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Walker l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Anh.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Perisic go hoa 1-1\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Perisic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Ivan-Perisic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Croatia-vs-Anh-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Walker m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a Perisic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, Walker ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn Anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu 11m, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 c\u0169ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Walker kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSouthgate \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai l\u1eddi th\u1ec9nh c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Walker \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 2 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u00ednh Walker kh\u00f4ng k\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perisic \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 John Stones kh\u00f4ng theo k\u00e8m Mandzukic \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pickford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Walker \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 b\u1edfi anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ivan Perisic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-1-4-1. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Croatia vs Anh </span>ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Perisic l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n (7 l\u1ea7n), anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Croatia (3 l\u1ea7n).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic da co 4 ban o cac ky World Cup\" title=\"Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ph\u00fat 68, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Sime Vrsaljko, Perisic b\u0103ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi Ph\u00fat 109, Perisic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Jordan Pickford \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Croatia. V\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, Perisic x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIvan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 ghi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Davor Suker (6) ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIvan Perisic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh: &ldquo;20 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang ng\u1ee1 m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 v\u1eady. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra qu\u00e1 nhanh khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n s\u1edbm Tam s\u01b0 c\u00f3&nbsp;th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i sau \u0111\u00f3 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh thua Croatia 1-2\" title=\"Anh thua Croatia 1-2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia 1-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Anh \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 khi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Croatia. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia khi\u1ebfn Anh n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Euro v\u00e0 World Cup anh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i (Euro 1968 vs Nam T\u01b0, World Cup 1990 vs \u0110\u1ee9c, Euro 1996 vs \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 vs Croatia).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia 2-1 Anh<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Croatia 2-1 Anh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia 2-1 Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Thong-so-Anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia 2-1 Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1153","checkdouble":"190994"},{"date":"06:13 12/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/14.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Croatia t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed nh\u01b0 m\u1edf h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf Moscow, hay xa h\u01a1n \u1edf ch\u00ednh qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 khi \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup.\r\n\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-DT-Croatia-lam-nen-lich-su-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Anh bay t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Croatia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong khi do, cac CDV Croatia dieu hanh qua nhieu tuyen pho o Moscow truoc tran dau.\" title=\"Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Croatia di\u1ec5u h\u00e0nh qua nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 \u1edf Moscow tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/060302-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Croatia di\u1ec5u h\u00e0nh qua nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed1 \u1edf Moscow tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"cen